description: Paramount Resources Ltd., an independent energy company, explores for, develops, produces, and markets natural gas, crude oil, and natural gas liquids in Canada. The company's principal properties are the Montney and Duvernay developments located in Alberta and British Columbia. It also invests in public and private corporations. Paramount Resources Ltd. was founded in 1976 and is based in Calgary, Canada.
ceo: Mr. James H. T. Riddell BSc, MSc (Geology)
